Mail-OpenRelay-Simple version 0.01
==================================

This module permit to check if a mail server runs as an open relay.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

   Net::Telnet

